      "sc:description": "Sherlock-Genome is an R Shiny application designed for genomic analysis and visualization, specifically tailored for cancer genomics studies. It facilitates data harmonization, interactive visualization, and integrative analysis of whole genome sequencing data, following FAIR principles.",
